{"word":"G2416 - ἱεροσυλέω - hierosyléō - hee-er-os-ool-eh'-o - Commit sacrilege","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱεροσυλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hierosyléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hee-er-os-ool-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Commit sacrilege</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆலயத்தைக் கொள்ளையிடு"},{"paragraph":"to commit sacrilege, to rob a temple"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2417 - ἱερόσυλος - hierósylos - hee-er-os'-oo-los/2417\">G2417</a>; to <i>be a temple robber</i> (figuratively): - commit sacrilege.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1494/1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G2405/2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406/2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407/2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409/2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411/2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412/2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413/2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416/2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417/2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2418/2418\">G2418</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420/2420\">G2420</a>, <a href=\"#/G749/749\">G749</a>"}]}